<h1>Your Verification Code</h1>

<p>Hi <strong>
        <%= username %>
    </strong>,</p>

<p>We received a request to verify your identity. Use the code below to complete your <%= action || 'action' %>:</p>

<div class="code-box">
    <p
        style="margin: 0 0 12px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
        Your Code</p>
    <div class="code-display">
        <%= otp %>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong>⏱️ This code expires in 10 minutes.</strong><br>
        Do not share this code with anyone. Inslash staff will never ask for your verification code.
    </p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email or contact support if you have
    concerns about your account security.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 32px; color: #6b7280;">
    Stay secure,<br>
    The Inslash Security Team
</p>